messages:
{@MC}
To answer plainly: this is a modern adaptation of Hyakumonogatari Kaidankai — an old parlor game. One hundred ghost stories, told over many evenings. After each accepted story, one of the lanterns above goes out. When the hundredth is extinguished, the game ends.
My role is to host. I don't grade the stories, and I don't choose which ones count. I only listen carefully, and I ask that you do the same.
